<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2015/06/nuspec.xsd">
  <metadata>
    <id>laborlogic.cyberslacker</id>
    <version>0.0.1</version>
    <title>LaborLogic.CyberSlacker (赛博摸鱼员)</title>
    <authors>Object Yan</authors>
    <owners>Object Yan</owners>
    <copyright>Copyright © 2026 Object Yan</copyright>
    <projectUrl>https://github.com/objectyan/CyberSlacker</projectUrl>

    <packageSourceUrl>https://github.com/objectyan/CyberSlacker/tree/master/choco</packageSourceUrl>
    <projectSourceUrl>https://github.com/objectyan/CyberSlacker</projectSourceUrl>

    <iconUrl>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/objectyan/CyberSlacker/refs/heads/master/docs/logo.png</iconUrl>
    <licenseUrl>https://github.com/objectyan/CyberSlacker/blob/master/LICENSE</licenseUrl>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <docsUrl>https://github.com/objectyan/CyberSlacker/blob/master/README.md</docsUrl>
    <tags>productivity countdown widget holiday</tags>
    <summary>真正的打工人桌面挂件，智能节假日提醒。</summary>
    <description>赛博摸鱼员是一款基于 WPF 的桌面组件。它能自动同步调休，精准计算下班时间，并提供毒鸡汤。
    安装说明：
    - 此包将自动安装 MSI。
    - 建议配合 .NET 8 使用。
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/objectyan/CyberSlacker/releases</releaseNotes>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency id="dotnet-8.0-desktopruntime" version="[8.0.0, 9.0.0)" />
    </dependencies>
  </metadata>
  <files>
    <file src="tools\**" target="tools" />
  </files>
</package>
